Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graham_Quirk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graham_Quirk\"}, {\"begin\": 852, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999950503025, \"rank\": 4.939698361130118e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"John has advised he has declined - with no further comment,\\\" an Australian Olympic Committee spokesman said.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comment was sought from Senate committee chairman Matt Canavan, who requested Coates's attendance at next week's hearing in Brisbane.\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1010, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"score\": 0.999999675706529, \"rank\": 3.242902649349092e-07, \"text\": \"Senate\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\"}, {\"begin\": 1036, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Canavan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Canavan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Canavan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Canavan\"}, {\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999950503025, \"rank\": 4.939698361130118e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coates has been the driver of the International Olympic Committee's \\\"new norm\\\" for selecting host cities, which encouraged them to use pre-existing facilities.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Archipelago founding director Peter Edwards, whose Brisbane Bold vision first mooted a stadium at Victoria Park, said Coates's role needed scrutiny.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1312, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Edwards_(rugby_league)\", \"score\": 0.42073926059475664, \"rank\": 0.66481994459836, \"text\": \"Peter Edwards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Edwards_(rugby_league)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Edwards_(rugby_league)\"}, {\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999950503025, \"rank\": 4.939698361130118e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It'd be great to understand how people like John Coates are actually providing advice to the process, as his focus seems to be on a demonstrated evidence of his new way of delivering the Olympics, which is 'do not build anything',\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\", \"score\": 0.999999982621148, \"rank\": 8.83850175013811e-09, \"text\": \"John Coates\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now that might be fine for London, Tokyo, Paris, LA - those major cities have had their significant moments of growth, but our city has to double in size by 2040 and we need to be using this moment to deliver the important infrastructure for our future.\\\"\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9991761145075622, \"rank\": 0.0008201018260098207, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999996095994, \"rank\": 1.7563385106196728e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1718, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999686810956, \"rank\": 3.1318865391197386e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brisbane would be the first city to host a Games under the new norm, and Coates reportedly told the Quirk review he was concerned the Olympic brand was being damaged by public disquiet over the projected$2.7 billion cost of the Gabba rebuild.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1932, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999950503025, \"rank\": 4.939698361130118e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.140713164573612e-17, \"text\": \"Gabba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That disquiet led to Miles announcing the review, inone of his first acts as premier-in-waiting.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A few weeks later,Miles appointed Quirk, a stalwart of the LNP, to lead the 60-day review, whichwas handed down last month.\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2333, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.57082302238846e-22, \"text\": \"LNP\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liberal_National_Party_of_Queensland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It recommended the Gabba rebuild be scrapped in favour of a $3.4 billion stadium to be built in a corner of inner-city Victoria Park, which was being repurposed from a golf course to public green space.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2418, \"end\": 2423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.140713164573612e-17, \"text\": \"Gabba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Gabba\"}, {\"begi