://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland_Sport_and_Athletics_Centre\"}, {\"begin\": 3209, \"end\": 3240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3272, \"end\": 3283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\", \"score\": 0.999999982621148, \"rank\": 8.83850175013811e-09, \"text\": \"John Coates\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_H._Coates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quirk was also asked to appear before the inquiry when it sits in Brisbane at the Hotel Grand Chancellor next week.\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3362, \"end\": 3370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999950503025, \"rank\": 4.939698361130118e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy to co-operate with any inquiry that the Senate might be having and so, yes, I will certainly be appearing,\\\"Quirk said.\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3465, \"end\": 3471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"score\": 0.999999675706529, \"rank\": 3.242902649349092e-07, \"text\": \"Senate\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Senate\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have reached your maximum number of saved items.\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3597, \"entities\": 